Renderforest -- a good site with premade animations that you can stitch together to make a clip

Types : 2d, 3d, Claymation, Traditional Hand Drawn, HTML animation, Animated Typography

 12 principles of animation...

        indicate weight
        transistions
        things dont stop at once
        add that touch of flair
        stretch and squish
        center..orient things .captures the attention
        show intention
        basic movements but with panache
        things move in arcs
        more drawings at ends fewer at the center indication of speed

